{"tid":296134,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"日本手造眼鏡Dita","createTime":"2017-06-24T10:37:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-26T20:41:44.000Z","uid":37306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"98da6fde46f463edf994ca490426721beb748cc5","tid":296134,"uid":37306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T10:37:16.000Z","msg":"想請教有玩開既師兄<br />\n呢個牌子係咪全部都係人手造㗎？<br />\n我睇中副union 2068 a blk/gld<br />\n但上面只係寫住made in Japan<br />\n希望有師兄可以分享下"},{"pid":"9998e557a9ac8509138a8fa853cddcc60095ade4","tid":296134,"uid":37306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T16:15:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f2aa0c60a5a9ef02472aac0d7c1be1219f2f705","tid":296134,"uid":36970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T19:47:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n去warehouse 慢慢試"},{"pid":"f134680b92ca789da7552336fbeb434d20b2ba1a","tid":296134,"uid":37306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T01:49:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n去warehouse 慢慢試</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我試過 睇過實物<br />\n但係見到上面寫既係made in Japan<br />\n唔係hand made in Japan<br />\n所以想問一問巴打們其實佢係唔係每一款都係手造<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f9adea3b47